config LIBCFS
	tristate "Lustre common library (libcfs)"
	help
	  libcfs is a foundational library shared by Lustre and LNet. It
	  provides portable utilities, debug and tracing infrastructure,
	  and compatibility shims used by the rest of the Lustre stack.

	  LIBCFS is required by LNet and Lustre and is normally selected
	  automatically when either is enabled.

	  To compile as modules, choose M here.

	  If unsure, say N.
